[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0543","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0543.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0328","title":"SGI IRIX 6.4 permissions 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 操作系统中的 permissions 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，成功利用后可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0328"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.827","remediation":"SGI IRIX 6.4 已停止维护多年，建议立即升级到不受影响的 IRIX 6.5 或更新版本；若无法升级，可临时移除 permissions 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/permissions）以阻断提权路径，但可能影响正常权限管理功能。终极方案是迁移至仍受支持的 Linux 或现代 Unix 系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19318"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0543.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0542","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0542.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0327","title":"SGI IRIX syserr 本地文件破坏漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统的 syserr 程序存在文件处理缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该程序以系统权限破坏或覆盖任意文件，导致系统不稳定或拒绝服务。该漏洞仅需本地用户账户即可触发，无需特殊权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0327"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.697","remediation":"立即应用 SGI 安全公告 19971103-01-PX 提供的官方补丁。由于 SGI IRIX 已于 2013 年底停止技术支持，长期建议迁移至仍在维护的 Linux 或 BSD 操作系统。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 `chmod 755 /usr/sbin/syserr` 移除 setuid 权限位，并通过 `chgrp` 将 syserr 程序组改为仅受信任的管理员组，限制普通用户执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0542.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0403","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0216","title":"Linux Kernel inetd SYN/RST Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 版本的 inetd 超级服务守护进程存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标主机发送特制的 SYN 和 RST 数据包，导致 inetd 服务异常终止或资源耗尽，无法正常响应合法连接请求。该漏洞影响运行 inetd 服务的 Linux 系统，攻击者无需认证即可实施攻击，且无需目标系统上存在特定监听服务。利用方式简单，通过发送大量伪造的 TCP SYN/RST 包即可触发，属于典型的网络层拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0216"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.917","remediation":"建议将 legacy inetd 替换为 xinetd，并在配置中设置 per_source = 5、cps = 25 30、max_load = 3 以限制并发连接和速率。或者迁移至 systemd socket 激活机制，利用内核 SYN cookies（sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1）和 iptables/nftables 限制入站 SYN 包速率（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -m limit --limit 10/s -j ACCEPT）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0216.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2bbcf0ff-3ba8-4c91-aea6-e3d5fdb0e178.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/linux.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0536","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0536.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0322","title":"FreeBSD open() 函数本地任意文件写入漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统的 open() 函数存在权限检查缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以提升的权限向任意文件执行写入操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 FreeBSD 系统，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限。由于漏洞利用需要本地账户，CVSS 评分仅为 2.1，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0322"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.983","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 系统至 3.0-RELEASE 或更高版本，该版本已修复 open() 系统调用中因缺乏权限检查导致的任意文件写入问题。如无法升级，可通过 sysctl 设置 kern.securelevel=1 提高内核安全等级，限制非 root 用户对敏感文件的 open 调用，并严格管控本地用户的可信度。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6092"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0536.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0228","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0097","title":"IBM AIX FTP 客户端命令注入漏洞","description":"AIX FTP 客户端在处理来自恶意 FTP 服务器的响应时存在命令注入漏洞。攻击者通过在 FTP 协议响应中嵌入 shell 元字符（如管道符 |），当用户连接至攻击者控制的 FTP 服务器时，恶意内容被传递给 shell 执行，导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可完全控制受害系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0097"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.750","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3.3 及以上维护版本，或安装 IBM APAR 安全补丁（IX72452 / IY07246）。如无法升级，可使用 OpenSSH sftp 替代 ftp 命令进行文件传输，或在 /usr/bin/ftp 上通过 chmod 移除不必要的执行权限以限制使用。避免使用 AIX ftp 客户端连接不可信或不受控的 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0097"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0221","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0221.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0094","title":"IBM AIX piodmgrsu 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统中 piodmgrsu 命令存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用该命令对用户组权限验证的缺陷，在未获得授权的情况下获取额外的用户组权限，从而扩大系统访问范围，执行越权操作。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0094"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.320","remediation":"安装 IBM 提供的对应 APAR 补丁（如 IX66020），或移除 piodmgrsu 命令的 setgid 权限（chmod g-s /usr/bin/piodmgrsu），并限制仅授权管理员可执行，防止本地用户利用此命令获取额外组权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0221.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0219","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0093","title":"IBM AIX nslookup 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统自带的 nslookup 命令在执行过程中未能正确清除提升的特权，导致本地普通用户可通过调用该命令获得 root 权限。攻击者只需拥有系统本地访问权限即可利用此漏洞，无需身份认证或用户交互。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 发行版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级 AIX 操作系统至厂商已修复的最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0093"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.180","remediation":"建议立即安装 IBM 针对此漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（IX73355），将 bos.net.tcp.client 文件集更新至 4.3.2.0 或更高版本。临时缓解措施可移除 nslookup 命令的 setuid root 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/nslookup。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0217","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0092","title":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 portmir 本地缓冲区溢出与不安全的临时文件创建漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 系统中的 /usr/bin/portmir 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制超长参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址以执行任意代码；同时该命令还存在不安全的临时文件创建问题，攻击者可利用符号链接竞争条件劫持临时文件实现提权。本地攻击者在拥有普通用户权限的条件下即可利用此漏洞获得 root 权限，影响 IBM AIX 4.2.1 及更早版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0092"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.030","remediation":"立即升级至 IBM AIX 5.1 及以上受支持版本，该问题已在后续版本中得到修复。如无法升级，以 root 执行 chmod 0755 /usr/bin/portmir 去除 setuid 位，并移除其他用户执行权限：chown root:system /usr/bin/portmir；同时在 /etc/security/sysck.cfg 中移除 portmir 条目标记。临时缓解措施可将需要 portmir 功能的用户加入专用组，通过 sudo 授权最小权限使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0092","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0092","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4be848c8-03f3-452a-a9ce-ef9613324759.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0214","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0214.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0091","title":"IBM AIX writesrv 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 writesrv 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该命令提交特制的输入参数触发溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构以获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，危害等级高，利用前提是攻击者具有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0091"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.873","remediation":"安装 IBM AIX APAR IX68518 补丁或升级至 AIX 4.3.3 及以上维护级别。如无法立即打补丁，可移除 writesrv 命令的 setuid root 权限执行 `chmod 0500 /usr/sbin/writesrv`，或通过文件权限控制限制非 root 用户执行该命令作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0091"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0214.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0181","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0072","title":"IBM AIX xdat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 xdat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 xdat 程序发送特制的超长输入参数，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用，成功利用后可完全控制受影响的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0072"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.907","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 为该漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（对应 AIX 4.x 及更早版本的 xdat 缓冲区溢出修复），或升级到包含该修复的 AIX 维护级别。临时缓解措施：执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/xdat` 移除 xdat 的 setuid root 权限，阻止非授权用户以 root 权限执行该程序；如业务不需要 DMI（Desktop Management Interface）子系统，可卸载相应文件集或禁用 xdat 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0072"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0169","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0169.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0068","title":"PHP PHP/FI mylog 脚本任意文件读取漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 的 mylog CGI 脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制的 URL 参数，读取目标服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 1.0、FI 2.0 及 FI 2.0 b10 版本，利用方式简单，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0068"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.230","remediation":"立即移除服务器上 PHP/FI 1.0/2.0 的 mylog/mlog CGI 脚本文件，或升级至 PHP 3.0 及以上版本，该漏洞在后继版本中已修复。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中禁止对该脚本的外部访问，并将 PHP/FI 替换为受支持的 PHP 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3396","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19553","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0068","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0068.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j2h3-fmf6-5vc4/GHSA-j2h3-fmf6-5vc4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/php_arbitrary_file_access.nasl","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/PHP_FI%201.0_2.0%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-0068).html","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0068.yaml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0169.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0169.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0169.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0375","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0375.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0192","title":"RedHat Linux telnetd TERMCAP 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Telnet 守护进程中的 tgetent() 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 TERMCAP 环境变量，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 RedHat Linux 6.0 及 Slackware Linux 4.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0192"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:51.540","remediation":"立即禁用 telnet 服务：编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 telnet 行后重启 inetd（或执行 service telnet stop），升级到不再提供 telnetd 的现代发行版；迁移至 SSH（OpenSSH）替代远程管理。如必须保留 telnet，可安装 TCP Wrapper 配置 hosts.allow/hosts.deny 限制源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0192","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19465","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0192.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/x0rz/EQGRP/blob/0c2354ff1073099b2aa417030b3167ec29d7279c/README.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0192","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0192.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0375.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0567","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0346","title":"PHP PHP/FI mlog 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0346 是 PHP 的 mlog CGI 脚本中存在的一个任意文件读取漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标服务器上该脚本发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用参数注入的方式读取服务器上的任意敏感文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），导致信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 PHP 版本，攻击条件低（无需认证、远程利用）。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0346"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.993","remediation":"升级至 PHP 3.0.17 或更高版本（已修复该 CGI 漏洞），或删除/禁用服务器上的 mlog CGI 脚本。若无法升级，请在 Web 服务器配置中禁止执行 /cgi-bin/php/fi/mlog 等路径，并设置文件系统权限限制 CGI 进程仅访问必要目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3397","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0346","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0346.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-misc.rules","https://github.com/mtesauro/owasp-wte/blob/e4c016caf67d59634f309f2a1feeed7dc9515abe/temp-projects/spikeproxy/contents/opt/owasp/spikeproxy/scan_database.db","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/php_arbitrary_file_access.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0160","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0160.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0061","title":"BSD Line Printer Daemon (lpd) 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"BSD 行式打印机守护进程（lpd）存在远程代码执行漏洞，源于其对打印任务处理过程中缺乏充分的访问控制与输入验证。远程攻击者无需认证即可向运行 lpd 服务的目标系统发送特制的打印请求，实现任意文件创建、删除或远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Linux 及 BSD 系列操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0061"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.180","remediation":"禁用 lpd 服务（`killall lpd` 并移除启动项），升级到已修复版本，或使用 TCP Wrapper 限制端口 515 仅允许受信主机访问；对于不需要网络打印的系统，建议直接卸载 lpd 替代为 CUPS 或 LPRng 等现代打印系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0061"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0160.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0541","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0326","title":"HP HP-UX mediainit 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 mediainit 媒体设备初始化程序存在安全漏洞。该程序用于初始化磁带机等存储设备，但由于对输入参数缺乏充分验证，本地攻击者可利用该缺陷，通过向 mediainit 程序传递特制参数触发漏洞，导致系统机密信息部分泄露、系统数据被部分篡改或服务部分不可用。此漏洞为本地利用，无需额外认证，攻击复杂度低，影响 HP-UX 系统多个版本，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。HP 已通过安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0326"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.543","remediation":"立即应用 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供的官方补丁。如无法打补丁，可移除 mediainit 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/mediainit），并限制可执行权限仅授予信任的管理员用户组。建议将 HP-UX 系统升级至包含该修复的后续版本（如 11.0 以上），因 10.x 系列已终止技术支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9710-071"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml"}]